Arik Air has introduced a sales promotion that will enable its frequent flyer program, Affinity Wings, members to purchase miles for traveling across the airline’s domestic network. In a statement sent to The Ameh News and endorsed by Adebanji Ola, PR and Communications Manager of the airlines sayings Tagged, Buy Miles & Fly, is the promotion targeted at new and existing Arik Affinity Wings members who can buy miles to fly to any of the airline’s destinations in the economy class cabin and earn additional 50% bonus miles. According to him, the promotion is available for sale from April 01, 2022 for travel between April 15 and May 15, 2022. Arik Air’s Chief Executive Officer, Captain Roy Ilegbodu commented: “We value our customers and that explains why they are always the focal point of our operations. Our products are designed to make travel easy and convenient for them”. Customers wishing to take advantage of the Buy Miles & Fly promo are to contact affinitywings@arikair.com or log on to www.arikair.com for more details.